OL,7,FThe grandparents of Ethan Ives-
OL,8,FGriffiths have been sentenced to life
OL,9,Fimprisonment for his murder.
OL,11,FHis grandfather Michael Ives must
OL,12,Fserve a minimum of 23 years before he
OL,13,Fwill be eligible for parole, while his
OL,14,FGrandmother Kerry Ives must serve at
OL,15,Fleast 17 years.
