OL,7,FEthan was two-years-old when he died
OL,8,Ffrom a catastrophic brain injury, just
OL,9,Fdays after he collapsed in the living
OL,10,Froom at the home of his grandparents
OL,11,FMichael and Kerry Ives, in Flintshire
OL,12,Fin August 2021.
OL,14,FThe pair, originally from
OL,15,FWolverhampton, were found guilty of
OL,16,Fmurder and child cruelty in July this
OL,17,Fyear after a trial at Mold Crown Court.
