OL,7,FHis mother Shannon Ives, who was
OL,8,Fliving with her parents at the time,
OL,9,Fwas also found guilty of causing or
OL,10,Fallowing his death and child cruelty.
OL,12,FShe has today been sentenced to 12
OL,13,Fyears in prison. She will Serve two
OL,14,Fthirds in custody and the remainder on
OL,15,Flicence
OL,17,FHanding down their sentences judge Mr
OL,18,FJustice Griffiths described how the
OL,19,Fdefendants had a campaign to "break"
OL,20,Fthe little boy's spirit.
