OL,5,CGriffiths
OL,7,F"Ethan was a 2 year old with an
OL,8,Findependent spirit. His mother and
OL,9,Fgrandparents hit him but he would
OL,10,Flaugh. He was a brave and resilient
OL,11,Fboy. The people hitting him didn't
OL,12,Flike the little boy sticking up to
OL,13,Fthem. They decided to hit him.
OL,15,F"You his grandparents murdered him.
OL,16,FYou his mother allowed that death"
OL,18,FThe six-week trial heard that Ethan
OL,19,Fwas severely underweight and
OL,20,Fdehydrated when he died, with 40
OL,21,Fvisible marks on his body.
