OL,7,FIn today's sentencing Ethan's father,
OL,8,FWilliam Griffiths, read out a victim
OL,9,Fimpact statement. He said: "I feel
OL,10,Fthat we are finally able to grieve his
OL,11,Fpassing knowing the persons
OL,12,Fresponsible are being held accountable
OL,13,Fin this court today and justice for
OL,14,FEthan will be served."
