OL,5,CGriffiths
OL,7,F"Although Ethan will be remembered
OL,8,Fmainly for what he was subjected to by
OL,9,Fhis own mother and grandparents who
OL,10,Fwere the people in his life that were
OL,11,Factually meant to love and care for
OL,12,Fhim, I want him to have his own voice
OL,13,Fand be remembered for the smiley,
OL,14,Foutgoing loving child that he was."
OL,16,FNicola Rees, from the Crown
OL,17,FProsecution Service, said: "This case
OL,18,Fhas been one of the most shocking I
OL,19,Fhave dealt with as a prosecutor.
