OL,5,CGriffiths
OL,7,F"The CCTV evidence showing how Ethan
OL,8,Fwas singled out and abused was
OL,9,Fharrowing. The acts of cruelty, both
OL,10,Fphysically and emotionally, were on a
OL,11,Flevel rarely seen."
OL,13,FShe added: "Being grandparents and a
OL,14,Fparent, the three defendants should
OL,15,Fhave cared for and protected Ethan,
OL,16,Fbut they did not. Our thoughts remain
OL,17,Fwith Ethan's father and family who
OL,18,Fhave suffered a heart-breaking loss."
