OL,7,FIn a statement, North Wales
OL,8,FSafeguarding Board said: "(Our
OL,9,Fmembers) wish to express their
OL,10,Fcondolences to the friends and family
OL,11,Fof Ethan who have been affected by his
OL,12,Ftragic death."
OL,14,FIt added: "Now that those responsible
OL,15,Ffor Ethan's death have been brought to
OL,16,Fjustice, the Safeguarding Board will
OL,17,Fcontinue with the Child Practice
OL,18,FReview."
OL,20,FThe review is expected to be completed
OL,21,Fby the start of 2026.
